。」开发人员必须在 14 天内更新应用以符合苹果商店的规则，否则可能会被下架。 《金融时报》报道中还提到中国开发人员设计了两种 CAID，一种是基于用户的 IP 地址，另一种基于电话的 IMEI，IMEI 是唯一的设备标识号。苹果认定收集这两种信息都是违反隐私规定的。 补充：苹果隐私政策迎重大调整 中国广告巨头研究应对方案金融时报：苹果警告部分中国科技公司不要规避应用追踪透明度规则 - IT 之家"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-4f924eae8b10a27e1e436d3a433efabf_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/450309264"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Isu2CqpqMs8VEEAMaCDYyMzQ3ODUyIN7r1YIGMG843hZALnIJNDUwMzA5MjY0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1616400396.4435532", "card_id": "Q_355023430", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 66}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果真的像《斗罗大陆》里一样有武魂的话，你希望自己是个什么武魂？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "只有一个就好，没双生别贪心。魂力限定在一环，能比普通人强一点但不至于超人满天飞。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-2ede1207f698043b3fe69bbf36824e7c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/355023430"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Isu2CqpqMs8VEEAMaCDQxMTcxOTMwIL2umu4FMAA4Z0AvcgkzNTUwMjM0MzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1616400396.443876", "card_id": "Q_277340935", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 304}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "男生真喜欢一个女生会有什么样的表现？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-3ed173437024a8ba59ff005b09c7cd7f_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/277340935"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Isu2CqpqMs8VEEAMaCDIzOTA3MDMzIJi+7dcFMAY4qw9AMHIJMjc3MzQwOTM1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_161640039